    <item>
      <title>斯塔默计划修改法律，简化英国与欧盟规则的衔接</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/starmer-plans-law-change-to-simplify-uk-alignment-with-eu-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·史塔默政府计划修改英国法律，使其更容易与欧盟的产品标准保持一致，这是国王演讲中提出的立法议程所包含的重大转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/starmer-plans-law-change-to-simplify-uk-alignment-with-eu-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 15:14:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚总统蒂努布要求参议院增加 38 亿美元支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/nigeria-s-tinubu-asks-senate-to-boost-spending-by-3-8-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚总统博拉·蒂努布要求立法者允许非洲最大原油生产国增加支出 6.2 万亿奈拉（38 亿美元），用于资助基础设施项目和其他优先事项。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/nigeria-s-tinubu-asks-senate-to-boost-spending-by-3-8-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 15:12:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登的主要捐赠者仍然希望他下台，但这比以往任何时候都更加困难</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/top-biden-donors-still-want-him-out-but-it-s-tougher-than-ever</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于一些民主党捐助者来说，对唐纳德·特朗普的暗杀企图并没有改变对乔·拜登总统连任竞选的考量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/top-biden-donors-still-want-him-out-but-it-s-tougher-than-ever</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 15:11:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民主党不会在八月前正式提名拜登</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/democrats-won-t-hold-virtual-roll-call-on-biden-before-august</link>
      <description><![CDATA[民主党至少要等到 8 月份才会通过网络点名的方式正式提名总统乔·拜登，因为一些人对此表示强烈抗议，他们认为提名过程是在拜登的授意下仓促进行的，目的是为了阻止要求他下台的呼声。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/democrats-won-t-hold-virtual-roll-call-on-biden-before-august</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 14:40:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
